webskillet14 theme
Customizations by Jonathan Kissam

1) rename folder to newthemename
2) rename webskillet14.info to newthemename.info
3) do a global search and replace for "webskillet14" to newthemename in the following files:
	newthemename.info
	template.php
	theme-settings.php
4) change name & description (& made any other pre-install edits) in newthemename.info
5) change or delete logo.png, logo-on.png, favicon.ico and add screenshot.png if desired
6) find and replace colors: #1280c9 (blue, used for links) and #cc0000 (red, used for hover links and error messages), #333 (for text), #999, #bbb, #ccc, #dddddd, #eee and #f5f5f5 (grays used for various shadings)

